          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-741O-line-1" n="1">Here Sarum Lies,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-741O-line-2" n="2">of late as wise,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-741O-line-3" n="3">As learn'd as Tom Aquinus;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-741O-line-4" n="4">Lawn Sleeves he wore,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-741O-line-5" n="5">yet was no more,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-741O-line-6" n="6">a Christian than So·cinus</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-741O-line-7" n="7"><lb/>Oaths Pro and con,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-741O-line-8" n="8">He Swallow'd down,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-741O-line-9" n="9">Lov'd Gold Like any Layman;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-741O-line-10" n="10">Who Preach'd &amp; Pray'd,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-741O-line-11" n="11">and yet Betray'd,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-741O-line-12" n="12">Gods Holy Church for mammon.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-741O-line-13" n="13"><lb/>of every Vice,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-741O-line-14" n="14">he had a Spice,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-741O-line-15" n="15">Altho a Reverend Prelate,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-741O-line-16" n="16">Yet Liv'd and dy'd,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-741O-line-17" n="17">if not Bely'd,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-741O-line-18" n="18">A true Dissenting Zealot.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-741O-line-19" n="19"><lb/>If such a soul,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-741O-line-20" n="20">To Heaven be Stole,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-741O-line-21" n="21">And Scap'd old Satan Clutches;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-741O-line-22" n="22">We'll then presume</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-741O-line-23" n="23">Ther may be roome</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-741O-line-24" n="24">For M──────────h<lb/>And his D──────────s</l>
          </lg>
